metadata.name: Nothing There to See
metadata.description:
-Nothing There to See-

Do not venture off the path
The well intended plea
False opinions back to back
There's nothing there to see

Do you feel it? That draw within you that beckons a certain path? Your vision may not be seen by others but it is yours to craft and bring forth.

1/1 digital piece that is the result of years of devotion making physical floral with personally restored Victorian Era tools that were long cast aside by society. This floral has been paired with AI reinterpretation. 

A true collaboration of passion, antiquity and the modern advances in art.
